NK015(ba)019:1: chos nyid gdal khyab chen po'i pho brang nas //
NK015(ba)019:2: dpal ldan kun bzang rdo rje 'chang chen dang //
NK015(ba)019:3: gsang ba'i bdag po tsa byi dri med ba dang //
NK015(ba)019:4: pra ti ha lo in+d+ra b+hu d+hi dang //
NK015(ba)019:5: ro lang bde ba d+ha na sam tri dang //
NK015(ba)019:6: pad+ma 'byung gnas mkha' 'gro mtsho rgyal dang //
NK015(ba)019:7: dpal gyi mchod gnas stag gi rdo rje dang //
NK015(ba)019:8: klu'i rgyal mtshan byang chub shes rab dang //
NK015(ba)019:9: ye shes dbang phyug byang chub rdo rje dang //
NK015(ba)019:10: byang chub tshul khrims ga ljang dbang phyug dang //
NK015(ba)019:11: gye re grags pa sho mang can pa'i zhabs //
NK015(ba)019:12: rdo rje rgyal mtshan dam pa bde gshegs dang /
NK015(ba)019:14: / 'gro mgon gtsang pa byams chos rnam gnyis dang //
NK015(ba)019:15: spyan dang zhang ston rnam gnyis ye shes 'bum //
NK015(ba)019:16: byang chub dpon po byang chub rdo rje dang //
NK015(ba)019:17: sang ga gu ru badz+ra sh+r+ai dang ni //
NK015(ba)019:18: b+hun+d+ha b+ha dra bkra shis bla ma dang //
NK015(ba)019:19: dz+ny+aa na ke du d+har+m+aa rat+na dang //
NK015(ba)019:20: badz+ra ku ma ra yi lha tshogs dang //
NK015(ba)019:21: phyi nang chos skyong dam can rgya mtsho'i tshogs //
NK015(ba)019:22: bdag cag gus pa'i yid kyis gsol 'debs na //
NK015(ba)019:23: bar chad zhi zhing bdud las rgyal ba dang //
NK015(ba)019:24: dam can rgya mtsho'i tshogs rnams bka' nyan cing //
NK015(ba)019:25: phrin las rgya mtsho ma lus 'grub pa dang //
NK015(ba)019:26: dngos grub rgya mtsho'i tshogs rnams 'byung ba dang //
NK015(ba)019:27: rdo rje'i sku thob don gnyis lhun grub shog /
NK015(ba)019:28: phur brgyud kyi gsol 'debs bsdus pa 'di /
